Class com.chimu.form.mapping.MappingPack 

java.lang.Object
   |
   +----com.chimu.form.mapping.MappingPack
public class MappingPack
extends Object
MappingPack contains the FORM Object-Relational mapping classes. See ObjectMapper, ObjectRetriever, Slot, and other classes for documentation of the FORM classes.

The MappingPack contains some Functors which have been moved into com.chimu.kernel.utilities.TranslationLib

See Also:
ObjectMapper, ObjectRetriever, Slot, TranslationLib
